description.narrative: MOHSW, LGAs and Shehias strengthen community health structures and communication strategies for promoting health and nutrition behaviours, which contributes to Child Health, Community-Based Management Of Acute Malnutrition, Infant And Young Child Feeding, Maternal And Newborn Health. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Improved and equitable use of high impact MNCH and nutrition interventions and promotion of healthy behaviours and nutrition practices
